```

Find the line for the Anthropic key (it'll look like `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=` or similar) and paste your key:
```
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=# Database
DATABASE_URL="postgresql://contract_intel:contract_intel_dev@localhost:5432/contract_intel?schema=public"

# NextAuth
NEXTAUTH_URL="http://localhost:3000"
NEXTAUTH_SECRET="your-nextauth-secret-here"

# Google OAuth
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID="your-google-client-id"
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET="your-google-client-secret"
